'''(1580) 拜突利亞''' ([[天文學臨時編號#小行星|臨時名稱]]：'''1950 KA''') 是1950年5月22日由[[Ernest_Leonard_Johnson|Ernest Leonard Johnson]]在[[南非|南非]][[約翰尼斯堡|約翰尼斯堡]]的[[聯盟天文台|聯盟天文台]]發現的一顆[[阿莫爾型小行星|阿莫爾型小行星]]。(1580) 拜突利亞的形狀被精確的測量：這顆小型最寬之處是6.59 ± .66公里，然而他的有效直徑是5.39±.54公里<ref name=aricebo>{{Cite journal | title = Radar observations and a physical model of Asteroid 1580 Betulia | last = Christopher | first = Magri | coauthors = et al. | journal = [[Icarus_(journal)|Icarus]] | volume = 186 | issue = 1 | date = 2007 | pages = 152–177 | url = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6WGF-4M5WJ2X-4&_user=10&_rdoc=1&_fmt=&_orig=search&_sort=d&view=c&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=94a18e044990be5a18f543e32f76cf62 | doi = 10.1016/j.icarus.2006.08.004 | bibcode = 2007Icar..186..152M | access-date = 2011-10-07 | archive-date = 2019-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190304132923/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6WGF-4M5WJ2X-4&_user=10&_rdoc=1&_fmt=&_orig=search&_sort=d&view=c&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=94a18e044990be5a18f543e32f76cf62 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

名稱是用來向天文學家[[Samuel_Herrick_(astronomer)|Samuel Herrick]].的妻子，拜突利亞·托羅表達敬意。Herrick曾經研究這顆小行星的軌道，並且要求以拜突利亞命名，之後還有[[小行星1685|(1685) 托羅]]<ref>Lutz D. Schmadel, [http://books.google.com/books?id=uwGbkbhMVyAC&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_v2_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q&f=false ''Dictionary of Minor Planet Names: Addendum to Fifth Edition: 2006 - 2008''] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=uwGbkbhMVyAC&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_v2_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20131231224639 }}.</ref><ref>University of California, [http://content.cdlib.org/view?docId=hb9k4009c7;NAAN=13030&doc.view=frames&chunk.id=div00024&toc.depth=1&toc.id=&brand=calisphere Samuel Herrick, Engineering; Astronomy: Los Angeles] {{Wayback|url=http://content.cdlib.org/view?docId=hb9k4009c7;NAAN=13030&doc.view=frames&chunk.id=div00024&toc.depth=1&toc.id=&brand=calisphere |date=20181122135737 }}</ref>。

